#

Wild Mushroom Risotto with Truffle Oil

40 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main CourseVegetarian

Tags:

Comfort FoodItalianEasy

Description

A creamy and luxurious risotto infused with earthy wild mushrooms and a hint of decadent truffle oil.

Ingredients

  • arborio rice: 1 cup
  • wild mushrooms (such as shiitake, oyster, or chanterelle): 2 cups, sliced
  • vegetable or chicken broth: 4 cups
  • onion: 1 small, diced
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • truffle oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley: for garnish
